{
  "stem": "25639.7",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And because she had either a Jewish husband or a Jewish boyfriend, which-- whom she did not wish to leave, and so he sent her to Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So-- and I understand that there were many famous, well-known women, particularly from France, who were incarcerated in Ravensbruck.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were a lot of artists.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were very helpful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I can't remember exactly what I did there, but I do remember this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We worked in some factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I know that there were a lot of women.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was there for a very short time and I was in very bad shape by this time, so no wonder that my memory isn't as clear as it-- as it could be.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The SS wanted us to increase our volume.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they went about it in a very interesting way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They issued some sort of coupons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that if-- they told a group that, if you-- mainly French women-- that if you finish a certain quantity of work, then we will give you certain coupons valued a certain amount and you can go and buy yourselves things with it.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now, I've never heard this in a camp, in any of the other camps, because Jews were not exposed to this.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was really one of the very few Jews among us, very few Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were thousands of us, many thousands.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And so-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they received coupons for having done a lot of work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I need a little more time for that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
